<i>noun</i>: 진작 [진ː작], 장려 [장ː녀], 독려 [동녀], 권장 [권ː장], 권면 [권ː면], 고취 [고취], 고양 [고양], 고무 [고무], 격려 [경녀] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>진작 [진ː작]</dt><br>
<dd>boost; encouragement</dd><br>
<dd>기운이나 정신을 북돋워 강하게 일으킴.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of energizing someone or boosting his/her spirit.</dd><br>
<dt>장려 [장ː녀]</dt><br>
<dd>encouragement</dd><br>
<dd>좋은 일을 하도록 권하거나 북돋아 줌.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of asking or encouraging someone to do good deeds.</dd><br>
<dt>독려 [동녀]</dt><br>
<dd>encouragement</dd><br>
<dd>일이 잘못되지 않도록 살피며 격려함.</dd><br>
<dd>Encouragement to make sure that the work is successfully completed.</dd><br>
<dt>권장 [권ː장]</dt><br>
<dd>recommendation; encouragement</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 권하고 장려함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of advising and encouraging someone to do something.</dd><br>
<dt>권면 [권ː면]</dt><br>
<dd>encouragement</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 하도록 힘써 권하고 충고함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of encouraging and advising a person to do something.</dd><br>
<dt>고취 [고취]</dt><br>
<dd>inspiration; encouragement</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 마음, 의욕 등이 강해지도록 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of strengthening someone's thinking, mind, will, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>고양 [고양]</dt><br>
<dd>boosting; encouragement</dd><br>
<dd>정신이나 의식 등을 높임.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of boosting another's spirit or raising awareness.</dd><br>
<dt>고무 [고무]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gomu</dd><br>
<dd>북을 치며 춤을 추는 한국의 전통 무용.</dd><br>
<dd>A traditional Korean dance, using buks, drums.</dd><br>
<dd>2. encouragement; inspiration; stimulation</dd><br>
<dd>무엇을 하고자 하는 마음이 생기거나 어떤 일이 일어나도록 하는 자극.</dd><br>
<dd>A stimulus encouraging someone to do something or something to happen.</dd><br>
<dt>격려 [경녀]</dt><br>
<dd>encouragement</dd><br>
<dd>용기나 의욕이 생기도록 기운을 북돋아 줌.</dd><br>
<dd>Cheering or buoying up someone to grant courage or motivation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>